{"tid":330161,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"aco/ca 小丑神祈禱區","createTime":"2017-07-21T02:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T03:19:54.000Z","uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0bedde261d3586aff4ad2c1c5b8f1b53689be3f2","tid":330161,"uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/88/NewClownGodcopy.jpg/revision/latest?cb20060825124231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F88%2FNewClownGodcopy.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb20060825124231&h=74fb488a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們在膠登的神， <br />\n<br />\n願人都尊神的名為膠； <br />\n<br />\n願神的國降臨； <br />\n<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上， <br />\n<br />\n如同行在高登。 <br />\n<br />\n我們日用的膠幣， <br />\n<br />\n求神今日賜給我們。 <br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠， <br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕假膠的人。 <br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探， <br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離耶教。 <br />\n<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、 <br />\n<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。膠們。 <br />\n<br />\n] <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj